      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty. It's seriously in pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every little detail. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the crazy dealership sticker shock, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions or come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 45500.0,
