    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Turbo, featuring the legendary 3.6L Mezger twin-turbocharged flat-six. This example is in concours-level condition, retaining its original factory paint and a pristine interior free of bolster wear. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and a sophisticated all-wheel-drive system, delivering visceral power with mechanical purity. Technical highlights include a factory dry-sump lubrication system, recently pinned coolant pipes for preventative longevity, and a flawless DME over-rev report. This is a turn-key, zero-modification specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands a peak-performance analog experience.",
